DeathStar is quite happy to learn that Dreadplague wishes to become his student.

DeathStar: It would be an honor...

Then DeathStar comes into visual contact with the Minions.

DeathStar: Well, Dread, there is the source of those signals. Do you want to observe them or introduce ourselves?

Lunekill was about to fly off when she caught sight of the incoming Tripredacus.

Lunekill: Curiosity killed the Cybertronians.

Lunekill extends her arm, her long, claw like finger tips glowing. She unleases several unknown energy blasts at Dreadplague and DeathStar.

Lunekill: DIE YOU PATHETIC VERMON!!!!!!!!!!

DeathStar sees the incoming shots.

DeathStar: Dread, evasive!

The star fighter barral rolls out of the way...

DeathStar: DeathStar, TRANSFORM!

Now in bot mode, DeathStar was ready to defend himself but their orders were not to engage the enemy under any circumstances.


